  "40pi m^2/min": "",
  "200pi m^2/min": "",
  "10pi m^2/min": "",
  "A = pi*r^2. dA/dt = 2pi*r*(dr/dt) = 2pi(20)(0.5) = 20pi m^2/min.": "",
  "A conical pile of sand has a height that is always twice the radius. Sand is added at 3 m^3/min. How fast is the height increasing when h = 4 m?": "",
  "3/(16pi) m/min": "",
  "12/(pi) m/min": "",
  "3/(4pi) m/min": "",
  "3/(pi) m/min": "",
  "h = 2r, so r = h/2. V = (1/3)pi*r^2*h = (1/3)pi*(h/2)^2*h = pi*h^3/12. dV/dt = pi*h^2/4 * dh/dt. 3 = pi(16)/4 * dh/dt = 4pi * dh/dt. dh/dt = 3/(4pi) m/min.": "",
  "A boat is pulled toward a dock by a rope attached to the bow 1 m above the water. If the rope is pulled in at 2 m/s, how fast is the boat approaching the dock when 5 m of rope is out?": "",
