  "A streetlight is 12 m high. A person 2 m tall walks away at 1.5 m/s. How fast is the tip of their shadow moving along the ground?": "",
  "2.0 m/s": "",
  "1.8 m/s": "",
  "0.3 m/s": "",
  "1.5 m/s": "",
  "By similar triangles: 12/(x+s) = 2/s, so 12s = 2x + 2s, 10s = 2x, s = x/5. The tip moves at d/dt(x+s) = d/dt(x+x/5) = (6/5)(dx/dt) = (6/5)(1.5) = 1.8 m/s.": "",
  "A plane flies overhead at 500 km/h at an altitude of 10 km. How fast is the distance from you to the plane changing when the plane is directly 10 km horizontally from you?": "",
  "500 km/h": "",
  "500/sqrt(2) km/h": "",
  "250*sqrt(2) km/h": "",
  "250 km/h": "",
  "d^2 = x^2 + 10^2. When x = 10: d = sqrt(200) = 10sqrt(2). 2d(dd/dt) = 2x(dx/dt). 20sqrt(2)*(dd/dt) = 2(10)(500) = 10000. dd/dt = 10000/(20sqrt(2)) = 500/sqrt(2) = 250sqrt(2) km/h.": "",
  "A trough is 10 m long with triangular cross-sections that are 2 m across the top and 1 m deep. Water is pumped in at 0.5 m^3/min. How fast is the water level rising when the water is 0.5 m deep?": "",
  "1/10 m/min": "",
  "1/5 m/min": "",
  "0.5/10 m/min": "",
  "1/20 m/min": "",
  "By similar triangles: w/h = 2/1, so w = 2h. Cross-sectional area = (1/2)(2h)(h) = h^2. V = 10h^2. dV/dt = 20h*(dh/dt). 0.5 = 20(0.5)*(dh/dt) = 10*(dh/dt). dh/dt = 1/20 m/min. Wait -- let me recheck: 0.5 = 20(0.5)*dh/dt = 10*dh/dt, so dh/dt = 0.05 = 1/20 m/min.": ""
